{
  "stem": "18932.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 470.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he felt that she would be better off being in a nursing home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was very happy there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember even before the war, I used to-- right into the war-- in the war in the beginning, I used to bring her some food every Saturday, and I used to talk to all the ladies.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to send-- you know, save for me chestnuts, because they liked me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I always used to come like the Little Red Riding Hood with the-- with the food for her grandmother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, grandma was about 89 or so, 90, like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she was very lucky, because grandmother died a natural death about a week, or maybe it was a couple of weeks, before they-- the German came to the nursing home.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They murdered all the-- all the people in the nursing home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't-- I-- I didn't go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I guess in Poland there was a custom that if you have your parents you weren't supposed to go to a funeral.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a Jewish custom.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When you have living parents you're not supposed to go to the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even when they say the holy prayer, when there was Yizkor, you used to-- you have to get out, because-- if you had living parents.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, they don't believe this anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They tell you you can stay on even there is the [INAUDIBLE], the prayers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She-- she did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was-- the-- the-- the cemetery was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was in a part-- was called, I think, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But she didn't stay too long there because she passed on, which was really lucky for her.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
